**PM Kisan Samman Nidhi - Complete Information**

**Objective:** To provide income support to all landholding farmers families in the country

**Eligibility:** All landholding farmers families, Small and marginal farmers, Family should have cultivable land

**Benefits:** ₹6,000 per year in three equal installments of ₹2,000 each

**Documents Required:** Land records, Aadhaar card, Bank account details, Mobile number

**Application Procedure:** Visit nearest Common Service Centre (CSC), Submit required documents, Fill the application form, Get application receipt

**Contact Information:** PM-KISAN Helpline: 1800-180-1551
**Official Website:** https://pmkisan.gov.in

**Mahatma Gandhi National Rural Employment Guarantee Act - Complete Information**

**Objective:** To provide at least 100 days of guaranteed wage employment in a financial year to every rural household

**Eligibility:** Adult members of rural households, Willing to do unskilled manual work, Should be registered in the job card

**Benefits:** Minimum wage as per state rates (₹200-₹350 per day)

**Documents Required:** Job card, Aadhaar card, Bank account details

**Application Procedure:** Apply for job card at Gram Panchayat, Submit required documents, Get job card issued, Demand work from Gram Panchayat

**Contact Information:** MGNREGA Helpline: 1800-345-3240
**Official Website:** https://nrega.nic.in
